(8, 1, '2016-09-28 19:14:22', '2016-09-28 19:14:22', '<h2>Find Out What Our Customers Are Saying</h2>\r\nYou can always count on Current Electrical to provide superior electrical service for your home or business. Since 2002 we’ve been assisting our Spokane neighbors with their residential and commercial projects. Our friendly, experienced staff has always ensured customer satisfaction – and loyalty. Just read some of these testimonials from our biggest supporters:\r\n<h3>What Homeowners Have to Say:</h3>\r\n<ul class="testimonials-interior">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="quotes-interior">“If you are in need of an outstanding electrician to show up to your home, call CEI! These guys are FANTASTIC! They don''t gouge you on cost. They do fast, outstanding work, and are just awesome people in general”</p>\r\n<p class="clients">- Brady P.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="quotes-interior">“I just could not be happier with the service we received from CEI. From the moment they picked up the phone they were the epitome of professionalism. The gentleman that answered my call, actually spent time talking with me about our issue. Even though I didn''t fully understand what I needed to have done, he did. The electrician that came to our home was courteous, punctual, professional and wearing a clean uniform emblazoned with his and the company names. He explained the work he was doing and the fees were very reasonable. I would absolutely recommend this business.”</p>\r\n<p class="clients">– Sattva R.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Call us today at 509-928-2522 and let our staff of friendly, licensed electricians get started on your next electrical or lighting project!</h4>', 'Testimonials', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'full-service-electrical', '', '', '2017-01-02 19:31:24', '2017-01-02 19:31:24', '', 12, 'http://ceispokane.com/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
