(139, 1, '2016-09-29 19:37:21', '2016-09-29 19:37:21', '<h1>The Most Trusted Electrical Contractor in Spokane</h1>\r\n<h2>Professional Service, Repair and Maintenance</h2>\r\n<p>Since 2002 Current Electrical has established a reputation as the most trusted electrical contractor in Spokane Washington. Through the years our family owned business has grown and flourished with the help of a dedicated team of professionals. Our experienced electricians, managers and team members have cultivated a strong relationship with our neighbors, built on trust and mutual respect. Quality work, same-day service and upfront pricing are hallmarks of our company, which continues to expand throughout Spokane and beyond.</p>\r\n<h3>Complete Electrical Services </h3>\r\n<p>Do you need a new light fixture replaced? Maybe surge protection for your new home? Current Electrical offers a wide array of professional electrical services from the simple to the complex. Our team of skilled electricians have the latest tools and experience to handle: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p><b>Electrical Troubleshooting </b></p>\r\n<p>If you have an electrical problem, but are not sure of the cause, our expert electricians can diagnose and repair the issue. Never let an electrical problem go unchecked. A frayed wire or compromised electrical system can easily become a fire hazard.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Repairs & Code Compliance</b></p>\r\n<p>Our master electricians can help with any residential electrical repair. They can also help update your electrical system to ensure code compliance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Panel Replacements & Upgrades</b></p>\r\n<p>Some older homes have electrical panels that are outdated, not the correct size for your system or sometimes both. We can help you with complete panel replacement or upgrade to ensure a safe, secure electrical system for your household.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Lighting</b></p>\r\n<p>In addition to complete electrical, we have a skilled staff of technicians who can help with all of your lighting needs. We can assist in all major areas of interior, exterior and landscape lighting. Whether it’s track lighting for your new entertainment room or outdoor flood lighting for safety and security, we can help light the way.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Backup Generator</b></p>\r\n<p>Ensure your home never loses power with whole-home surge protection. Keep your home and family safe during extended blackouts with continuous, uninterrupted power for extended periods.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Switches, Outlets & Dimmers</b></p>\r\n<p>Let our master electricians assist with the repair, installation or replacement of your electrical switches, outlets and dimmers. We have the tools and the experience to complete the project both quickly and efficiently.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Smoke & CO2 Detectors</b></p>\r\n<p>Ensure the safety of your home and family with up-to-date smoke and CO2 detectors for your home. We can provide expert insight into the proper placement for installation of both types of alarm systems.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Ceiling Fans</b></p>\r\n<p>Keep rooms cooler in the summer and warmer in the winter with a variety of ceiling fan designs. Our experts can help with the installation and replacement of any brand or style.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Wiring & Rewiring</b></p>\r\n<p>Our master electricians can assist with any residential wiring project. Whether you need wiring for a new room addition or have an old home that needs complete rewiring, we have the tools and experience to get the job done.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Electrical Safety Inspections</b></p>\r\n<p>Do you have a new home that needs an electrical inspection? Maybe your current home hasn’t had an inspection in over a decade? Our skilled electricians can assess your system and go over options for any necessary repairs or upgrades.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Call Current Electrical today at 509-928-2522 and let our master electricians get started on your next electrical project!</h4>', 'Electrical Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '76-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-29 19:37:21', '2016-09-29 19:37:21', '', 76, 'http://ceispokane.com/76-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
