(157, 1, '2016-09-30 14:44:09', '2016-09-30 14:44:09', '<h2>Ensure Your Electronic Equipment is Secure with Thermal Imaging Photography</h2>\r\n<p>When modern electrical equipment begins to fail, it will usually heat up before the problem manifests in more obvious ways. Thermal imaging technology makes those hot spots visible so that you can catch the problem and get it corrected before it is damaged beyond repair. This allows an electrician to safely investigate a variety of electrical equipment essential in the function and success of a business. Breaker panels, fuses, bolted connections, electrical cabinets and more can be scanned for an immediate picture of potential problems. Our master electricians have the skill and the experience to find and help solve the issue.</p>\r\n<h3>Thermal Imaging Electrical Inspections</h3>\r\n<p>Current Electrical can perform comprehensive electrical inspections on sensitive equipment components and commercial electronics. Thermal Imaging technology can help find hot spots with:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Electrical Panels</li>\r\n<li>Electrical Circuits</li>\r\n<li>Mechanical Equipment</li>\r\n<li>Heating and Cooling Equipment</li>\r\n<li>Various Electronics (Including Computers)</li>\r\n<li>Transformers</li>\r\n<li>Controllers</li>\r\n<li>Relays/Switches</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Skilled, High Tech Troubleshooting</h3>\r\n<p>Our experienced, licensed electricians can troubleshoot any commercial electrical problem you are experiencing. Continuous education and training ensures that our staff is proficient in the latest technologies – including thermal imaging inspections. A meticulous attention to detail and commitment to superior customer service drives our staff to find the solutions both quickly and efficiently. Our electricians are also committed to a clean, professional appearance; treating your business as they would their own.</p>\r\n<h4>When you need high tech troubleshooting for your commercial business, contact Current Electrical at 509-928-2522 for a variety of thermal imaging solutions.</h4>', 'Thermal Imaging', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'thermal-imaging', '', '', '2016-10-27 16:07:41', '2016-10-27 16:07:41', '', 136, 'http://ceispokane.com/?page_id=157', 0, 'page', '', 0),
