raining means we get it right the first time. We are available for 24-hour emergency service at no additional charge.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Safety</b></p>\r\n<p>All of our electricians are fully trained, drug tested, and background checked. We are exclusive partners with the Electric Safety Foundation International.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><p><b>Convenience</b></p>\r\n<p>Our friendly and knowledgeable electricians always arrive on time in a fully stocked vehicle for fast repairs and installations. A wide range of products and services means you only have to make one call.</p>\r\n</li>   \r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Whether it’s installing a ceiling fan or rewiring your entire building, Current Electrical is the trusted name for all your electrical needs. Call us today at 509-928-2522 to schedule an appointment!</h4>   ', 'Commercial Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '136-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-30 15:38:11', '2016-09-30 15:38:11', '', 136, 'http://ceispokane.com/136-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
