nstallation or replacement of your electrical switches, outlets and dimmers. We have the tools and the experience to complete the project both quickly and efficiently. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Smoke & CO2 Detectors </b>\r\n<p>Ensure the safety of your home and family with up-to-date smoke and CO2 detectors for your home. We can provide expert insight into the proper placement for installation of both types of alarm systems. </p>\r\n</li> \r\n\r\n<li><b>Ceiling Fans </b>\r\n<p>Keep rooms cooler in the summer and warmer in the winter with a variety of ceiling fan designs. Our experts can help with the installation and replacement of any brand or style. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Wiring & Rewiring </b>\r\n<p>Our master electricians can assist with any residential wiring project. Whether you need wiring for a new room addition or have an old home that needs complete rewiring, we have the tools and experience to get the job done. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Electrical Safety Inspections</b>  \r\n<p>Do you have a new home that needs an electrical inspection? Maybe your current WA residence hasn’t had an inspection in over a decade? Our skilled electricians can assess your system and go over options for any necessary repairs or upgrades. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3> Professional Troubleshooting for [city] Homes  </h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our master electricians are skilled troubleshooters who can help solve any residential wiring problem. Continuous education and training ensures that our staff is proficient in the latest technologies – as well as older wiring and components. A meticulous attention to detail and commitment to superior customer service drives our staff to find the solutions both quickly and efficiently. If you are having electrical problems in your [city] home, give the professionals at Current Electrical a call today!</p>\r\n<p>Our master electricians can help troubleshoot a variety of wiring problems including: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Voltage Spikes</li>\r\n<li>Short Circuits</li>\r\n<li>Light Fixtures </li>\r\n<li>Dead Receptacles</li>\r\n<li>Power Outages</li>\r\n<li>Underground Wiring</li>\r\n<li>Appliance/Electronics Shock</li>\r\n<li>Hot Outlets</li>\r\n<li>And More!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Let our master electricians find the solution to your [city] electrical problem. Call us at 509-928-2522 and we’ll schedule an appointment today! </h4>\r\n\r\n', 'Veradale', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'veradale', '', '', '2016-10-28 19:13:42', '2016-10-28 19:13:42', '', 217, 'http://ceispokane.com/?page_id=211', 0, 'page', '', 0),
