(243, 1, '2016-10-27 16:07:24', '2016-10-27 16:07:24', '<h2>Expert Lighting Installation and Lighting Control Solutions</h2>\r\n<p>Current Electrical knows how important lighting can be for a business. Both productivity and growth can be affected by poor lighting placement and improper fixtures. From handsome track lighting in a lobby to a combination of direct and indirect options for work areas, we have the experience to help light the way. Our master electricians can assess any space and recommend flexible, energy-saving light and light control solutions for every corner of the office.</p>\r\n<h3>Commercial Lighting Projects</h3>\r\n<p>Looking to make some changes in your office lighting? Maybe you are thinking about a complete renovation? Whether it’s a high level of indirect lighting for a computer work station or comprehensive task lighting for a meeting room, our licensed electricians can help with every step in the process. We can help identify the function of each work space and choose the best configuration and light fixture to enhance that purpose. We can also help recommend the appropriate light controls for each light installation to ensure maximum efficiency.</p>\r\n<p>Current Electrical’s licensed electricians are experts at:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Track Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Automatic Light Sensors</li> \r\n<li>Ambient Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Task Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Kitchen Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Recessed Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Ceiling Lights</li>\r\n<li>Light Dimmers</li>\r\n<li>Light Timers</li>\r\n<li>Utility Lighting</li>\r\n<li>Most Commercial Lights and Lighting Fixtures</li> \r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Over A Decade of Lighting Solutions</h3>\r\n<p>Since 2002 Current Electrical has established a reputation as the most trusted commercial lighting contractor in Spokane. Through the years our family owned business has grown and flourished with the help of a dedicated team of professionals. Our master electricians, have cultivated a strong relationship with our busine