(264, 1, '2017-01-02 19:50:41', '2017-01-02 19:50:41', '<h2>Experienced Electricians for All Your Electrical Concerns</h2>\r\nCurrent Electrical has been keeping Spokane businesses safe and secure for over a decade. Our master electricians are skilled troubleshooters who can help solve any commercial wiring or electrical problem. As a local business entrenched in the electrical industry, we have seen firsthand the destructive results from damaged equipment and systems. So it is imperative that any electrical problems be investigated and corrected before the day-to-day business is affected as well. Let our master electricians solve your wiring and electrical problems so that you and your staff can get back to business.\r\n<h3>Skilled Troubleshooting</h3>\r\nOur experienced, licensed electricians can troubleshoot any commercial electrical problem you are experiencing. Continuous education and training ensures that our staff is proficient in the latest technologies – as well as older wiring and components. A meticulous attention to detail and commitment to superior customer service drives our staff to find the solutions both quickly and efficiently. Our electricians are also committed to a clean, professional appearance; treating your business as they would their own.\r\n\r\nCurrent Electrical can help troubleshoot a variety of wiring problems including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Voltage Spikes</li>\r\n 	<li>Short Circuits</li>\r\n 	<li>Light Fixtures</li>\r\n 	<li>Dead Receptacles</li>\r\n 	<li>Power Outages</li>\r\n 	<li>Underground Wiring</li>\r\n 	<li>Appliance/Electronics Shock</li>\r\n 	<li>Hot Outlets</li>\r\n 	<li>And More!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>The Current Electrical Advantage</h3>\r\nWe’re dedicated to making every troubleshooting service call a successful one. When you choose Current Electrical, you will always receive superior work and our list of benefits:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Clean, Professional, Licensed Technicians</li>\r\n 	<li>Angie’s List Super Service Award-Winner Since 2001</li>\r\n 	<li>Combined 30 Years of Professional Experience</li>\r\n 	<li>Commitment to Customer Service Excellence</li>\r\n 	<li>Green Initiatives</li>\r\n 	<li>Nexstar Membership</li>\r\n 	<li>Straightforward Pricing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Let our master electricians find the solution to your electrical problem. Call us at 509-928-2522 and we’ll schedule an appointment today!</h4>', 'Troubleshooting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '148-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-02 19:50:41', '2017-01-02 19:50:41', '', 148, 'http://ceispokane.com/148-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(265, 1, '2017-01-02 19:51:52', '2017-01-02 19:51:52', '<h2>Professional Service, Repair and Maintenance</h2>\r\nSince 2002 Current Electrical has established a reputation as the most trusted electrical contractor in Spokane Washington. Through the years our family owned business has grown and flourished with the help of a dedicated team of professionals. Our experienced electricians, managers and team members have cultivated a strong relationship with our neighbors, built on trust and mutual respect. Quality work, same-day service and upfront pricing are hallmarks of our company, which continues to expand throughout Spokane and beyond.\r\n<h3>Complete Electrical Services</h3>\r\nDo you need a new light fixture replaced? Maybe surge protection for your new home? Current Electrical offers a wide array of professional electrical services from the simple to the complex. Our team of skilled electricians have the latest tools and experience to handle:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><b>Electrical Troubleshooting </b>If you have an electrical problem, but are not sure of the cause, our expert electricians can diagnose and repair the issue. Never let an electrical problem go unchecked. A frayed wire or compromised electrical system can easily become a fire hazard.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Repairs &amp; Code Compliance</b>Our master electricians can help with any residential electrical repair. They can also help update your electrical system to ensure code compliance.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Panel Replacements &amp; Upgrades</b>Some older homes have electrical panels that are outdated, not the correct size for your system or sometimes both. We can help you with complete panel replacement or upgrade to ensure a safe, secure electrical system for your household.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Lighting</b>In addition to complete electrical, we have a skilled staff of technicians who can help with all of your lighting needs. We can assist in all major areas of interior, exterior and landscape lighting. Whether it’s track lighting for your new entertainment room or outdoor flood lighting for safety and security, we can help light the way.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Backup Generator</b>Ensure your home never loses power with whole-home surge protection. Keep your home and family safe during extended blackouts with continuous, uninterrupted power for extended periods.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Switches, Outlets &amp; Dimmers</b>Let our master electricians assist with the repair, installation or replacement of your electrical switches, outlets and dimmers. We have the tools and the experience to complete the project both quickly and efficiently.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Smoke &amp; CO2 Detectors</b>Ensure the safety of your home and family with up-to-date smoke and CO2 detectors for your home. We can provide expert insight into the proper placement for installation of both types of alarm systems.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Ceiling Fans</b>Keep rooms cooler in the summer and warmer in the winter with a variety of ceiling fan designs. Our experts can help with the installation and replacement of any brand or style.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Wiring &amp; Rewiring</b>Our master electricians can assist with any residential wiring project. Whether you need wiring for a new room addition or have an old home that needs complete rewiring, we have the tools and experience to get the job done.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Electrical Safety Inspections</b>Do you have a new home that needs an electrical inspection? Maybe your current home hasn’t had an inspection in over a decade? Our skilled electricians can assess your system and go over options for any necessary repairs or upgrades.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Call Current Electrical today at 509-928-2522 and let our master electricians get started on your next electrical project!</h4>', 'Residential Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '76-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-02 19:51:52', '2017-01-02 19:51:52', '', 76, 'http://ceispokane.com/76-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
